</div><div class="col-title col-xs-12 col-md-10 pull-right"> <h1 class="pg-title" >
NATO Chief Warns US Congress of &#39;More Assertive Russia&#39;
</h1>
</div><div class="col-publishing-details col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-2 pull-left"> <div class="publishing-details">
<div class="published">
<span class="date" >
<time datetime="2019-04-03T07:23:52-04:00">
April 03, 2019 7:23 AM
</time>
</span>
<span class="date" >
<span class="badge badge--updated">update</span>
<time datetime="2019-04-03T14:14:00-04:00">
April 03, 2019 2:14 PM
</time>
</span>
</div>
<div class="links">
<ul class="links__list links__list--column">
<li class="links__item" >
Ken Bredemeier
</li>
</ul>
