</div><div class="col-title col-xs-12 col-md-10 pull-right"> <h1 class="pg-title" >
Trump Takes Credit for Turning Around NATO
</h1>
</div><div class="col-publishing-details col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-2 pull-left"> <div class="publishing-details">
<div class="published">
<span class="date" >
<time datetime="2019-04-02T17:15:28-04:00">
April 02, 2019 5:15 PM
</time>
</span>
<span class="date" >
<span class="badge badge--updated">update</span>
<time datetime="2019-04-03T05:51:00-04:00">
April 03, 2019 5:51 AM
</time>
</span>
</div>
<div class="links">
