</div><div class="col-title col-xs-12 col-md-10 pull-right"> <h1 class="pg-title" >
Iraqi Official: US Support Vital to Lasting IS Defeat
</h1>
</div><div class="col-publishing-details col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-2 pull-left"> <div class="publishing-details">
<div class="published">
<span class="date" >
<time datetime="2019-04-02T21:55:05-04:00">
April 02, 2019 9:55 PM
</time>
</span>
</div>
<div class="links">
<ul class="links__list links__list--column">
<li class="links__item" >
Rikar Hussein
</li>
<li class="links__item" >
<a class="links__item-link" href="/author/29567.html" title="Balen Saleh">Balen Saleh</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="col-lg-12 separator"> <div class="separator">
<hr class="title-line" />
</div>
